T01TD1111E:42b-1: sarba dznye ma h'a shva ra sto tram n'a ma /
T01TD1111E:42b-3: thams cad mkhyen pa dbang phyug chen po'i bstod pa zhes bya ba /
T01TD1111E:42b-4: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1111E:42b-5: gang zhig lha las lhag pa'i lha //
T01TD1111E:42b-6: de gang lha yi bla ma ste //
T01TD1111E:42b-7: bla ma'i bla mar gyur pa de //
T01TD1111E:42b-8: de la bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
T01TD1111E:42b-9: chen po nyid dang dbang nyid dang //
T01TD1111E:42b-10: gang zhig dbang phyug che nyid gyur //
T01TD1111E:42b-11: 'jig rten gsum las grol ba yi //
T01TD1111E:42b-12: dbang phyug tshe der bdag phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1111E:42b-13: ye shes me yi 'od kyis ni //
T01TD1111E:42b-14: 'dod dang rmongs pa'i rang bzhin gyi //
T01TD1111E:42b-15: grong kyer sum brtsegs zad bsregs pa'i //
T01TD1111E:42b-16: grong khyer gsum bsregs pa der 'dud //
T01TD1111E:42b-17: byams pa'i thod pa rtag 'chang zhing //
T01TD1111E:43a-2: tshul khrims zla bas dbu brgyan pa'i //
T01TD1111E:43a-3: dbang phyug tshe der bdag phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1111E:43a-4: byams dang snying rje'i rva mchog dang //
T01TD1111E:43a-5: dga' dang btang snyoms mig ldan pa'i //
T01TD1111E:43a-6: theg chen khyu mchog bcibs pa yis //
T01TD1111E:43a-7: gang zhig gshegs mdzad dbang phyug che //
T01TD1111E:43a-8: sbyin dang tshul khrims bzod brtson 'grus //
T01TD1111E:43a-9: bsam gtan la sogs btsun mo dang //
T01TD1111E:43a-10: mchog bcas tshogs kyis gshegs mdzad pa'i //
T01TD1111E:43a-11: dbang phyug che der bdag phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1111E:43a-12: g-yo yi rva yis kun du khyab //
T01TD1111E:43a-13: kun nas nyon mongs srid dbus zhig / phar 'gro'i srid bu mi bzad pa //
T01TD1111E:43a-14: lta ba 'bar ba rab bsregs can //
T01TD1111E:43a-15: dur khrod gang dgos thugs mnga' ba //
T01TD1111E:43a-16: rnam pa sna tshogs sprul pa'i gzugs //
T01TD1111E:43a-17: rtag tu tshogs bcas kyis 'khyud pa'i //
T01TD1111E:43a-18: dbang phyug che der bdag phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1111E:43a-21: bka' sgrub pa yis mi mchi ba'i //
T01TD1111E:43a-22: dbang phyug che der bdag phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1111E:43a-23: yan lag brgyad kyi tshul ldan zhing //
T01TD1111E:43a-24: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa'i sgrong skyes kyi //
T01TD1111E:43a-25: yongs bskor mi 'jigs chen po'i gling //
T01TD1111E:43a-26: sgo nyid g-yo ba rab tu dag / snying rje'i chu ni rgyu ba can /
T01TD1111E:43a-27: dam chos chu bo gang 'dzin pa //
T01TD1111E:43a-28: dbang phyug che der bdag phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1111E:43a-29: mi shes pa yi ma he yis //
T01TD1111E:43a-31: bsnun mdzad ye shes rtse gsum gyis //
T01TD1111E:43a-32: rtse gsum can gang dbang phyug che //
T01TD1111E:43a-33: mchog dang tha ma bar dag dang //
T01TD1111E:43a-35: ma zhi thams cad rnam grol ba'i //
T01TD1111E:43a-36: dbang phyug che der bdag phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1111E:43a-37: skye ba'i sdug bsngal ma lus pa //
T01TD1111E:43a-38: thugs rje mchog gi khyad par gyis //
T01TD1111E:43a-39: gang zhig gsal bar 'phrog pa yis //
T01TD1111E:43a-41: dbang phyug dam pa phun tshogs shing //
T01TD1111E:43a-42: 'dod pa'i chu la sred spangs pa //
T01TD1111E:43a-43: de la phyag 'tshal lha chen po //
T01TD1111E:43a-44: sems can thams cad bde mdzad pa //
T01TD1111E:43a-45: gang zhig kun gyi rjes 'brangs pas //
T01TD1111E:43a-46: sems can thams cad sdud pa yi //
T01TD1111E:43a-47: bdud kyi bgegs kyis mi thub pa'i //
T01TD1111E:43b-0: dbang phyug @43b dam pa chen po nyid //
T01TD1111E:43b-1: rab nyes spub pa skyes bu gang //
T01TD1111E:43b-2: de la phyag 'tshal lha chen po //
T01TD1111E:43b-3: sems can thams cad phan bzhed pa //
T01TD1111E:43b-4: gnod pa'i kun du dgrar gyur gang //
T01TD1111E:43b-5: byams pa yis kyang rnam zhen dang //
T01TD1111E:43b-6: dkar po'i chos kyang yongs rdzogs pa'i //
T01TD1111E:43b-7: dbang phyug tshe der bdag phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1111E:43b-8: gza' dang rims nad dbul ba dang //
T01TD1111E:43b-9: las kyis gzir ba'i 'gro ba dang //
T01TD1111E:43b-10: gsung tsam gyis myur zhi mdzad pa'i //
T01TD1111E:43b-11: zhi ba de la bdag 'dud do //
T01TD1111E:43b-12: 'jig rten kun gyi dbang phyug la //
T01TD1111E:43b-13: bstod pas bdag gis dge bsags pas //
T01TD1111E:43b-15: ye shes dbang phyug che gyur ci ba [?] //
T01TD1111E:43b-16: thams cad mkhyen pa dbang phyug chen po zhes bya ba'i bstod pa bram ze'i dge bsnyen mtho btsun grub rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T01TD1111E:43b-18: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po dz'a ran da na dang /
T01TD1111E:43b-19: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba rin chen bzang pos bsgyur ba'o /
